These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, water, 7up, iced-tea, coffee, sprite, almond-milk
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, satire, scientific, sports, musical, romance, spy
 1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 2. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching musical movies##2
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk | almond-milk | water    | 7up | coffee   | sprite    |
| Movie-Genre         | romance  | satire   | sports | crime | scientific   | spy | musical |

