.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, colonial, craftsman, wooden, tower, palace
7 different pets are kept: bird, fish, pony, dog, chinchilla, rat, snake
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the colonial house is between the tower house and the owner of the rat##2
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the palace house is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the ranch-style house is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
8. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| House          | wooden | colonial | tower | ranch-style | palace | futuristic      | craftsman  |
| Pet   | rat | dog  | snake     | pony     | chinchilla  | bird | fish |

