.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, bluemaster, siglo, blend, chaman, dannemann
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, dubstep, classical, reggae, gospel, blues, r&b
