 3. the fan gospel is the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the fan pop is on the left of the fan r&b##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the fan reggae##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the fan classical##1
 8. the fan pop is between the fan r&b and the siglo-smoker##2
 9. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the fan blues##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Cigar   | dannemann | blend | baccarat | alhambra   | siglo | bluemaster | chaman |
| Music-Genre           | gospel | blues     | dubstep     | classical | reggae   | pop   | r&b    |

