.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
House: wooden, ranch-style, art-deco, colonial, cape-cod, craftsman, victorian
7 different pets are kept: horse, fish, ferret, snake, goldfish, dog, cat
 1. the victorian house is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the wooden house##1
 6. the owner of the snake is between the art-deco house and the owner of the dog##2
 7. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the colonial house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is the owner of the fish##1
10. the owner of the horse is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| House      | art-deco    | cape-cod  | colonial  | wooden  | victorian      | craftsman       | ranch-style |
| Pet   | goldfish | snake | dog | cat | horse | ferret | fish  |

