The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, baseball, lacrosse, cricket, volleyball, biathlon, climbing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the davidoff-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the dunhill-smoker##1
9. the baccarat-smoker is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Cigar   | dunhill      | baccarat | vegafina | montecristo | davidoff      | tiparillo      | alhambra |
| Sport     | baseball | biathlon | climbing       | snowboarding | lacrosse | volleyball | cricket |

