5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsdahlia and the person drinking water##2
7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
8. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
